:{"origin":15550,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sadaqa: Giving charity is better than receiving it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe upper hand is better than the lower hand.\u00a0The upper hand is one that gives and the lower hand is one that takes.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1429, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1033 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1064,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/10\/23\/sadaqah-al-jariyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15550,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Death: His deeds end except knowledge, charity, offspring","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 23, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen the human being dies, his deeds end except for three: ongoing charity, beneficial knowledge, or a righteous child who prays for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1631 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u00a0\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1758,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/22\/plant-tree-reward-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":15550,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Every tree a Muslim plants is rewarded as charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo Muslim plants a tree or sows a seed and then a bird, or a human, or an animal eats from it but that it is charity for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2320, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3912,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/01\/two-malaikah-blessing-cursing\/","url_meta":{"origin":15550,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Angels: Two angels descend every day, blessing or cursing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere is not a day upon which the servant awakens but that two angels descend. One of them says: O Allah, repay one who spends in charity! The other says: O Allah, give destruction to one\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18862,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/04\/17\/every-muslim-does-this-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":15550,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Every Muslim who does these enter